that your father gave.

34:53.070 --> 34:56.639
It's a story I've
heard many times before.

34:56.706 --> 34:59.674
Unfortunate that his
pain was passed to you.

34:59.742 --> 35:01.509
So it ends here.

35:01.577 --> 35:04.110
I don't have children.

35:04.178 --> 35:06.278
Still, you passed it to others.

35:10.418 --> 35:12.486
Ted stoddard, ronnie kalen.

35:12.554 --> 35:15.222
I-I feel sure that my legacy

35:15.289 --> 35:18.790
Will justify some inconvenience

35:18.858 --> 35:19.891
To a few individuals.

35:19.958 --> 35:21.192
Your legacy?

35:21.259 --> 35:23.526
You're not gonna have
any legacy in science.

35:23.594 --> 35:24.694
Is that what you're talking about?

35:24.762 --> 35:27.262
