35:32.133 --> 35:33.566
When the time is right?
How about now?

35:33.634 --> 35:34.767
What's wrong with now? I'm here.

35:34.835 --> 35:36.301
I'm willing.

35:36.369 --> 35:40.704
Uh-huh, that's what I thought.

35:40.771 --> 35:42.205
Face it, you did two trials.

35:42.272 --> 35:44.606
