35:49.310 --> 35:52.111
But leland kalen died

35:52.179 --> 35:54.479
Refusing to shoot his wife.

35:54.547 --> 35:55.880
They cancel each other out.

35:55.948 --> 35:57.581
So, inconclusive.

35:57.649 --> 35:59.816
Bauhaus, is this?

35:59.884 --> 36:02.219
Bauhaus? Werkbund.

36:02.286 --> 36:06.021
My grandfather could build
bauhaus in his sleep.

36:06.089 --> 36:10.358
Ugh. The junk that passes
for quality these days.

36:10.426 --> 36:14.499
There's no artistry.
There's no structure.

36:14.567 --> 36:16.536
It's--it's meaningless.

36:16.604 --> 36:18.005
Meaningless.

36:18.072 --> 36:22.181
Yeah, well, that brings
us back to your theory.

36:22.248 --> 36:27.185
You know, the social
sciences nowadays,

36:27.253 --> 36:29.720
With the blogs and kooky websites,

36:29.788 --> 36:30.922
Motivational speakers.

36:30.989 --> 36:32.823
None of that has any
bearing on what I do.

36:32.891 --> 36:36.159
You can't bolster
flawed theory, abel.

36:36.227 --> 36:38.861
Kammerer, with miller,
with him, I'm sure,

36:38.929 --> 36:40.529
Doctored those toads

36:40.597 --> 36:42.531
In order to disprove evolution.

36:42.599 --> 36:45.033
Lysenko faked his
results under stalin,

36:45.101 --> 36:46.968
Had all his critics murdered.

36:47.036 --> 36:49.704
Flawed science is no science.

36:49.772 --> 36:53.574
But my results are definitive.

36:57.814 --> 37:00.182
If I'm such a monster,

37:00.249 --> 37:02.717
Aren't you a little afraid?

37:05.354 --> 37:07.022
No.

37:07.089 --> 37:08.957
My mistake was
thinking that actually

37:09.025 --> 37:11.192
You maybe had something to hide.

37:11.260 --> 37:14.062
But you got no proof.

37:15.831 --> 37:19.067
I have recorded data.

37:19.134 --> 37:21.970
It has been checked and rechecked.

37:22.037 --> 37:25.339
Come on, if you had it,
you'd show it.

37:25.407 --> 37:29.010
Your so-called
experiments were a flop.

37:29.078 --> 37:32.380
All right.

37:35.684 --> 37:38.185
All right.

38:25.328 --> 38:27.463
20 seconds.

38:27.530 --> 38:29.965
Ronnie, no, please. It's me!

38:30.032 --> 38:31.933
Ronnie, no, no, no, no, no, no!

38:32.000 --> 38:33.767
No, ronnie, no! - I'm sorry!

38:33.835 --> 38:36.303
Ronnie, no! Oh, god, no!

38:36.371 --> 38:39.239
aah!

38:42.609 --> 38:44.610
Proof.

38:46.412 --> 38:49.547
Was it enough?

38:52.317 --> 38:57.788
In true science,
repeatability is everything.

39:02.894 --> 39:04.561
It's okay.

39:04.629 --> 39:05.729
There.

39:05.797 --> 39:07.398
It's okay, it's okay.

39:07.465 --> 39:08.799
It's okay.

39:10.034 --> 39:10.968
Aah!

39:19.544 --> 39:22.679
All done under the most
stringent of circumstances.

39:22.747 --> 39:24.982
Nothing manipulated or altered.

39:25.049 --> 39:29.420
Age, sex, religion, income, race,

39:29.487 --> 39:32.156
All painstakingly factored in.

39:32.223 --> 39:35.159
Five years, nine different cities.

39:35.226 --> 39:37.894
Out of ten trials,

39:37.962 --> 39:40.897
Only one subject shows
selfless altruism

39:40.965 --> 39:45.102
And that was only
because of their age.

39:45.169 --> 39:47.170
Yeah. You know who
observed that also?

39:47.238 --> 39:49.239
The nazis.

39:49.307 --> 39:50.574
And they recorded it.

39:50.641 --> 39:52.542
Just like you, it's their legacy,

39:52.610 --> 39:55.445
Which you have successfully
carried forward.

39:55.513 --> 39:57.547
No. This is my work.

39:57.615 --> 39:58.815
Your work?

39:58.883 --> 40:01.751
Dr. Kogel could have shown us this.

40:01.819 --> 40:04.320
Dr. Mengele with his
experiments on twins.

40:04.388 --> 40:05.789
These are my validations.

40:05.856 --> 40:08.725
They had validations
at a cost of suffering

40:08.793 --> 40:10.293
And human lives.

40:10.361 --> 40:13.797
And what did their
experiments prove, abel, huh?

40:13.865 --> 40:16.099
The nazi scientists,
what did their experiments prove?

40:16.167 --> 40:17.367
You have no right to--

40:17.435 --> 40:19.102
I have every right to compare
you to your colleagues.

40:19.170 --> 40:20.236
That much you have proven.

40:20.304 --> 40:21.938
What did your nazi colleagues...

40:22.006 --> 40:23.206
Give to science?

40:24.642 --> 40:26.042
The same thing that
you've given to science.

40:26.110 --> 40:27.977
Nothing. - No.

40:28.045 --> 40:31.180
After all of my work,
you cannot compare me with them.

40:31.248 --> 40:34.350
Just because you've
been brutalized by others

40:34.418 --> 40:37.721
Does not mean that brutalizing
others is compulsory.

40:37.789 --> 40:39.189
Maniac.

40:39.257 --> 40:41.157
And what happened to your family

40:41.225 --> 40:44.326
Is too unfathomably
complicated to even go into.

40:45.995 --> 40:47.762
What is all this?

40:47.830 --> 40:49.230
Part of this moron's efforts

40:49.297 --> 40:52.633
To prove something that,
in science,

40:52.700 --> 40:55.835
Failed miserably,
but is gonna be of great value

40:55.903 --> 40:57.103
In convicting him of murder.

40:57.171 --> 40:59.071
No.

40:59.139 --> 41:02.574
I have proven selfless
behavior is a myth.

41:02.642 --> 41:03.975
No one has a choice.

41:04.043 --> 41:07.612
Tell him about his choices.

41:07.679 --> 41:09.680
You may choose to remain silent.

41:09.748 --> 41:11.081
It is your right.

41:11.149 --> 41:13.483
You may also choose a lawyer.

41:13.551 --> 41:17.687
If not, one will be
provided for you.

41:19.489 --> 41:21.524
Ronnie kalen didn't waste any time.

41:21.591 --> 41:23.292
Let me guess.
She wants a new trial?

41:23.360 --> 41:25.428
And damages for the
time she's already served.

41:25.495 --> 41:26.429
Yeah.

41:26.496 --> 41:28.064
Come on, she's guilty.

41:28.131 --> 41:30.132
Well, you know,
it's a valid question

41:30.200 --> 41:33.135
How anybody'll act under
those circumstances.

41:33.203 --> 41:35.338
Are you buying into
abel hazard's theory?

41:35.405 --> 41:37.240
