People rush into fires.

41:37.307 --> 41:38.841
They jump in front of trains.

41:38.909 --> 41:40.910
They leap into
shark-infested waters.

41:40.978 --> 41:42.612
Who doesn't want to think

41:42.680 --> 41:44.748
That they could
sacrifice their own life

41:44.815 --> 41:46.316
To save somebody else's?

41:46.384 --> 41:48.151
It goes to the core
of our humanity, but--

41:48.219 --> 41:50.287
But no one knows what they'd do

41:50.354 --> 41:52.189
Until something actually happens.

41:52.256 --> 41:53.290
Yeah.

